  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world is devastated, and survival is becoming less likely...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a survivor, you must fight to stay alive one more day and flee to wherever life is still possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How long will you be able to survive?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Outposts</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a nomad, you are not alone, and you can always trade with other survivors as well as collaborate by completing quests.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/87c649db688d42998fc2af4a8bae12a9.avif?t=1760886099\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras_big/87c649db688d42998fc2af4a8bae12a9.avif?t=1760886099 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/f08011c35033c47f07ac25ddeacb68bb.avif?t=1760886099\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras_big/f08011c35033c47f07ac25ddeacb68bb.avif?t=1760886099 width=800 height=450 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Looting</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loot the different scenarios and zombies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/1ae8b5dc0c372d7823f72af7b00a75c0.poster.avif?t=1760886099\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/1ae8b5dc0c372d7823f72af7b00a75c0.webm?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/1ae8b5dc0c372d7823f72af7b00a75c0.mp4?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Farming</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect materials from the environment to craft items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/6c3fc6dfa5b11561a5bb71782058ed66.poster.avif?t=1760886099\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/6c3fc6dfa5b11561a5bb71782058ed66.webm?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/6c3fc6dfa5b11561a5bb71782058ed66.mp4?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Crafting</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft items that allow you to survive, with a step-by-step system that penalizes errors by reducing the quality of the item in case of failure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/552982d9c043a8abe0a2e0ce4aa58237.poster.avif?t=1760886099\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/552982d9c043a8abe0a2e0ce4aa58237.webm?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/552982d9c043a8abe0a2e0ce4aa58237.mp4?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedural world</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape contamination through a world of procedurally generated maps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/00a58f17185c58de355ff64e1f883328.poster.avif?t=1760886099\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/00a58f17185c58de355ff64e1f883328.webm?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/00a58f17185c58de355ff64e1f883328.mp4?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Vehicles (with customizations)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Repair and customize vehicles that enable you to travel and be lethal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/45a1520bf965f15c39e0532cbcb22f74.poster.avif?t=1760886099\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/45a1520bf965f15c39e0532cbcb22f74.webm?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/45a1520bf965f15c39e0532cbcb22f74.mp4?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defense building</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fortify your position with walls and traps that have different effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/0baf18444d2f4bd85541aad3fcda5d80.poster.avif?t=1760886099\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/0baf18444d2f4bd85541aad3fcda5d80.webm?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/0baf18444d2f4bd85541aad3fcda5d80.mp4?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hordes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resist periodic hordes that intensify in number, strength, and speed over time and contamination level. You must be prepared for them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/b1e0dabe46e68adb18b754939f4ba050.poster.avif?t=1760886099\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/b1e0dabe46e68adb18b754939f4ba050.webm?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279180/extras/b1e0dabe46e68adb18b754939f4ba050.mp4?t=1760886099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
